I finished The Mime Order yesterday and was definitely disappointed since I LOVED The Bone Season. The sequel was just really slow for the plot, the characters were okay, the romance was bleh, but I did love the world even though we didn’t get to see too much of it. It’s just a mixed bag for me 😂. I am going to continue to The Song Rising though, just not anytime soon 😂.
📚
I started The Kingdom of Copper at midnight when I finished my homework, and it’s off to a good start from the prologue 🤩. I’m so excited to read more today! 😆
